  "tcmTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Also known as asparagus root, tianmendong is a sweet and bitter tasting herb that is very cold in nature, and enters the lung and kidney meridians. It is used to clear lung heat, nourish the yin and moisten dry areas of the body. It is a useful treatment for dry coughs, chronic respiratory disorders and symptoms such as a dry tongue and chronic thirst. The asparagus roots are harvested in winter, cleaned, steamed and peeled to produce this medicinal herb.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "天冬是百合科植物，藥用部份是塊根，藥味甘、苦，其性寒涼，歸屬肺、腎經，功能是養陰潤燥、清火、生津，常用於陰虛肺熱引起的燥咳、口乾、咽痛等，亦可改善腎陰不足導致的潮熱盜汗、內熱消渴等。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "天冬是百合科植物，药用部份是塊根，药味甘、苦，其性寒涼，歸属肺、肾经，功能是养阴润燥、清火、生津，常用于阴虚肺热引起的燥咳、口干、咽痛等，亦可改善肾阴不足導致的潮热盜汗、內热消渴等。\n"
